name: 约利马尔·拉拉
name_full: 约利马尔·拉拉 Yolimar Lara
introduction: Yoli Lara was born in Puerto Rico on January 26, 1994. At the age of 12, she began her studies at the Levittown Arts & Dance School of Puerto Rico , where she graduated with high honors. At the age of 15, she starred in her first campaign for Pantene (2009) directed by Rafael Rodriguez. A few tittles came after until she moved to Los Angeles, where she continued her film & modeling career, and started on TV. She has appeared on films such as Rebel Moon (2023), FIT (2022), Rhasberry Cream (2015).
